_sText:
My first map released into the wild (designed by my clanmate thunderschunked)

gg_thunder_arena is a fun, fast(ish) map with little room for camping.  Basically consists of three "floors" - a factory floor with ladders up to a rooftop where you can shoot down at the people below and a flooded basement underneath with multiple access points...  

We've run it on our servers and it's a lot of fun, so please try it out and let us know what you think.  As it is my first map, if I've done stuff wrong/badly, I would really like to know....
